OL,7,FTwo men have been sentenced for a
OL,8,Frange of terrorist offences including
OL,9,Fdeploying a wildlife camera to monitor
OL,10,Fand target a retired police officer.
OL,12,F56-year-old Damien Duffy from from
OL,13,FWestclare Court in Dungannon and 31-
OL,14,Fyear old Shea Reynolds from Kilwilkie
OL,15,FRoad in Lurgan were convicted of six
OL,16,Fjoint offences committed between
OL,17,FSeptember 3 and 21, 2016.
