OL,7,FAt Belfast Crown Court they were
OL,8,Fsentenced by Judge Patricia Smyth for
OL,9,Foffences she said were "committed in
OL,10,Fpursuit of violent Republicanism."
OL,12,FDuffy was handed an extended custodial
OL,13,Fsentence comprising of 12 years and
OL,14,Fsix months in prison with an extended
OL,15,Flicence period of five years.
OL,17,FAn extended custodial sentence of 11
OL,18,Fyears and six month in prison with an
OL,19,Fextended licence period of five years
OL,20,Fwas handed to Reynolds.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
