OL,7,FBoth men were also made the subject of
OL,8,Fthe Terrorist Notification Act for a
OL,9,F30-year period.
OL,11,FJudge Smyth said: "The specific
OL,12,Ftargeting of a retired police officer
OL,13,Fis a very grave matter.
OL,15,F"This involved a well researched plan
OL,16,Fto obtain information to enable an
OL,17,Fattack upon his life.
OL,19,F"The attempt to obtain that
OL,20,Finformation was only foiled by the
OL,21,Fpolice."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
