OL,7,F"The nature and the harm to which the
OL,8,Foffending was directed was to endanger
OL,9,Flife."
OL,11,FDuring the trial, it emerged that on
OL,12,Fthe evening of September 4, 2016 both
OL,13,Fmen were involved in deploying the
OL,14,Fwildlife camera on the Annaghone Road
OL,15,Fin Coalisland.
OL,17,FThey travelled from Lurgan to
OL,18,FCoalisland in a grey Volkwagon Golf
OL,19,Fdriven by Reynolds where they deployed
OL,20,Fthe device.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
