OL,5,Cofficer jailed
OL,7,FThe camera remained in place until
OL,8,FSeptember 8, 2016 when the pair
OL,9,Freturned to retrieve it.
OL,11,FIt was then deployed in the driveway
OL,12,Fof the home of a retired police
OL,13,Fofficer on September 14, 2016.
OL,15,FThe following morning, he spotted the
OL,16,Fitem and contacted the PSNI who
OL,17,Freplaced the camera with a dummy.
OL,19,FDuffy and Reynolds then returned to
OL,20,Fthe scene on September 20, 2016 and
OL,21,Fremoved what was now a dummy camera.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
