OL,7,FShe said that in her view Duffy and
OL,8,FReynolds were "not acting as lone
OL,9,Fwolves" which was based on evidence
OL,10,Fheard during the trial including a
OL,11,Fsimilar wildlife camera and manual
OL,12,Ffound in the homes of other suspects.
OL,14,FThe Judge added: "Both defendants have
OL,15,Fbeen convicted of being principal
OL,16,Fparticipants and there is no doubt of
OL,17,Fthe danger posed by those involved in
OL,18,Fdissident Republican activity who
OL,19,Fconsider serving and retired police
OL,20,Fofficers to be legitimate targets of
OL,21,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
