OL,7,F"Neither defendant has accepted
OL,8,Fresponsibility for these offences and
OL,9,Fno remorse has been shown."
OL,11,FDessie Hutton KC, representing
OL,12,FReynolds, pointed out there was "no
OL,13,Fcharge involving actual violence or
OL,14,Falleged membership".
OL,16,FRevealing his client, who has a clear
OL,17,Fcriminal record, has spend almost
OL,18,Fseven years on remand, Mr Hutton said
OL,19,FReynolds has used his time in custody
OL,20,F"fitfully".
