OL,7,FDuffy's barrister Brendan Kelly KC
OL,8,Fsaid that whilst his client has a
OL,9,Fterrorist conviction dating back to
OL,10,F1993, there was "no suggestion" Duffy
OL,11,Fhas re-offended since his arrest for
OL,12,Fthe offences involving the wildlife
OL,13,Fcamera.
OL,15,FMr Kelly also spoke of the "positive
OL,16,Fsteps" Duffy takes within his local
OL,17,Fcommunity which includes supporting
OL,18,Flocal sports.
